body:
Hi, I'm trying to use auto hot key in league. But regardless of the macro it simply does not work. It works on everything BUT league. I've tried simulating holding down the key for about 10ms and even 1000ms. But no matter what I try it doesn't work. Here's an example of what I've tried.

RButton::
Send {^4 down}
Sleep 15
Send {^4 up}
Send {RButton down}
Sleep 15
Send {RButton up}

PS: Its my dream to laugh on movement. Please help make someones dream come true <3
